      "title": "Perturbation methods in optimal control",
      "abstract": "The Principal Results of Deterministic and Stochastic Optimal Control Ergodic Control Regular Perturbations in Deterministic Optimal Control Regular Perturbations in Stochastic Optimal Control Singular Perturbations in Deterministic Optimal Control Singular Perturbations in Stochastic Control Bibliography."
    },
    "123003227": {
      "title": "Long-term average cost control problems for continuous time Markov processes: A survey",
      "abstract": "This paper addresses the long-term average cost control of continuous time Markov processes. A survey of problems and methods contained in various works is given for continuous control, optimal stopping, and impulse control."
    }
